headline: Amphenol Announces Third Quarter 2025 Dividend
summary: WALLINGFORD, Conn., July 31, 2025--Amphenol Corporation (NYSE: APH) announced today that its Board of Directors approved the third quarter 2025 dividend on its Common Stock in the amount of $0.165 per share at its meeting held on July 30, 2025. The Company will pay this third quarter 2025 dividend on October 8, 2025 to shareholders of record as of September 16, 2025.
